### M5 main boundary call
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/book-and-notify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "candidateId": 1,
  "slotId": 1001,
  "serviceId": 1
}

### Mock remote service directly
POST http://localhost:8080/mock-api/notifications/booking-confirmation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "BOOKING_CONFIRMED",
  "candidateId": 1,
  "slotId": 1001,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "deliveryChannel": "EMAIL",
  "message": "Your TechStride appointment has been booked successfully."
}
